  "description": "Simple hierarchy permission based spawn plugin!",
  "body": "<center>\n<br />\n\n<img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e62d0e5f366dae5a10a4'/>\n\n<img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e6b50e5f366dae5a10aa'/> <a href='https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/%E2%9A%A1-mtspawn-%E2%9A%A1-teammt-%E2%9A%A1.114364/updates'> <img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e6b50e5f366dae5a10b2'/> </a><a href='https://panel.masecla.dev/wiki/MTSpawn/'> <img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e6b50e5f366dae5a10b4'/> </a><a href='https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP'> <img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e6b50e5f366dae5a10a8'/></a>\n\n<img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e62d0e5f366dae5a10a6'/>\n\n<img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e61b0e5f366dae5a1092'/> <img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e62d0e5f366dae5a109b'/>\n\n<img src='https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/6599e5ae0e5f366dae5a1090'/>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/FdMjWSP\"><img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/image/638a91e9aa2989386ab8ef79\" /> </a>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Full transcript</summary>\n\nMTSpawn\n\nEasy to manage permission-based spawns!\n\nSPAWN\nA must have spawn plugin for server owners!\n\nThe plugin offers you a very simple way of managing your different spawns through simple in-game menus!\n\nAlways up to date with the game!\n\nCUSTOMIZABLE \nEvery aspect is configurable, without being overloaded!\nThis plugin integrates the fully customizable messages protocol. Send clickable components, make chat menus, send URL's and more!\n\nSPEED\nNever lose an ounce of performance when using our plugin!\n\nThe plugin uses an efficient way of checking player movement, which doesn't process hundreds of events!\n\nSEAMLESS GUI\nEasy to navigate GUI to change the ordering of the plugins!\n\nThe plugin will send each player to the highest spawn they have permission for!\n\nOrder is changed easily via GUI!\n\n</details>\n\n</center>\n\n<img src=\"https://panel.masecla.dev/api/v1/views/HiQ6Fw4DJw8_EyIDNwIACRscaTcmHwMDKh0MCRs\" />",
